Package: KruRooSocNet
Title: KruRoo Social Network Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Siwachoat", "Srisuttiyakorn", , "siwachoat.s@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-2723-0025"))
Description: A comprehensive package for social network analysis with a focus 
    on education and research applications. The package provides tools for both 
    global and local network analysis, including ego-network measures, centrality
    metrics, community detection, and visualization capabilities. 'thaisna' is 
    designed to work with both binary and valued network data, and integrates
    seamlessly with tidyverse packages.
